snippet.title: UpWakeNing - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official trailer for UpWakeNing, a precise jumping platformer available on Steam.

It is a game that puts your nerve to the limit. For every successful jump, the higher the stakes. Your patience will be put to the test.
Will you be able to reach to the top?

If you succeed, invite your friends to this challenge, and watch if they can succeed or enjoy their struggles!

You can wishlist #UpWakeNing on steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1410700/UpWakeNing/

Support us by liking the video and subscribe:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgPfLp0ONMM0pszOLPWs6UQ?sub_confirmation=1

This #indiegame is made by Pham Studio.

Join our discord: https://discord.gg/xHKbfuA

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/pham_studio

Visit the homepage here:
https://www.pham-studio.com
